        desc: "You thrive in chaos like a cat in a yarn factory. Multi-layered problems? Bring it on. If life hands you a Rubik‚Äôs cube, you solve it blindfolded while juggling flaming marshmallows. You laugh in the face of complexity and probably have a spreadsheet for your spreadsheets."
